Maria Sharapova Defeats Cibulkova to Advance to Semifinals at Wimbledon

-- B y   C h r i s   E l s e r
-- 
2011-06-28T16:06:43Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-06-28/maria-sharapova-defeats-cibulkova-to-advance-to-semifinals-at-wimbledon.html
Former champion  Maria Sharapova  lost
just two games in her victory over Dominika Cibulkova of
Slovakia to reach the semifinals of the Wimbledon tennis
tournament.  The 2004 winner took the match 6-1, 6-1 over the 24th
seeded Cibulkova, who was in her first quarterfinal at the All
England Club. Sharapova, the fifth seed, is now 12-3 in Grand
Slam quarterfinals.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Chris Elser at 
 celser@bloomberg.net  